nodes.text: Diana Kent is a South African actress who portrays General Engell in the 2019 film Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker. She played Kate Winslet's mother in Peter Jackson's psychological thriller Heavenly Creatures from 1994, and has played guest roles in British TV series such as Heartbeat, Midsomer Murders, New Tricks, Agatha Christie's Poirot and the 2012 miniseries Titanic.
